fcipExtMIB.description: The module defines management information specific to FCIP devices.

BrcdCompressionRatio.name: BrcdCompressionRatio
BrcdCompressionRatio.description: A number indicating a compression ratio over a set of bytes. The value is defined as a set of bytes. The value is defined as 1000 * bytes(compressed) / bytes(original) rounded to the next integer value. Note that compressed sets of bytes can be larger than the corresponding uncompressed ones. Therefore, the number can be greater than 1000.
